  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为'Biblioteca Personal Skill'画一个系统上下文图。这是一个帮助用户管理个人书籍的Alexa技能。核心角色是我们的用户，他通过语音与Alexa交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "Biblioteca Personal Skill",
        "alexa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以用户是'Usuario'，描述为'Usuario de la Biblioteca Personal Skill'。我想确认一下，Alexa本身在这个图里算一个独立系统，还是需要框起来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa",
        "alexa_boundary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Alexa应该放在一个叫'Amazon Alexa'的系统边界里。边界内部有两个东西：Alexa语音服务平台本身，还有我们的技能。这样结构更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alexa_boundary",
        "alexa",
        "skill"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，边界内包含'Amazon Alexa'语音服务平台和'Biblioteca Personal Skill'。技能描述是'Alexa Skill for managing books'，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alexa",
        "skill",
        "alexa_boundary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。现在说外部依赖——这个技能需要存储书籍元数据，还要存封面图片。元数据用DynamoDB做缓存，图片放S3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "skill",
        "ddb",
        "s3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "DynamoDB是'NoSQL Database'，S3是'Object Storage'。这两个都放在边界外面，作为外部数据库系统，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ddb",
        "s3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，它们是AWS基础设施，不属于Alexa生态内部。现在画关系：用户发语音命令给Alexa，Alexa回语音响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：用户到Alexa的'Comandos de voz'关系，以及Alexa返回给用户的'Respuestas de voz'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要一条'Uses'关系从用户指向Alexa，表示用户在使用这个平台。然后Alexa调用我们的技能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa",
        "skill"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了'Uses'关系和'Invokes Skill'关系。技能再往下连接S3和DynamoDB，都是'Uses'关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa",
        "skill",
        "s3",
        "ddb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，技能使用S3存图片，使用DynamoDB缓存书籍信息。两条都是'Uses'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "skill",
        "s3",
        "ddb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我检查一下：Person是Usuario，System_Boundary是Amazon Alexa，内部有Alexa平台和Biblioteca Personal Skill，外部有S3和DynamoDB。关系也都齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa_boundary",
        "alexa",
        "skill",
        "s3",
        "ddb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现一个问题。用户到Alexa的'Uses'关系是不是有点冗余？我们已经有了语音命令和响应的双向关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "在C4模型里，'Uses'表示使用关系，而'Comandos de voz'是具体交互。两者语义不同，建议保留。但如果要精简，可以去掉'Uses'只留具体标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "alexa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还是保留吧，这样符合C4标准。不过我想确认DynamoDB的名字——是叫'DynamoDB Cache'还是直接'DynamoDB'？我们内部常说是缓存层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ddb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "当前是'DynamoDB Cache'，描述为'NoSQL Database'。需要改成其他吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ddb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改，Cache能体现它的用途。S3那边是'Amazon S3'和'Object Storage'，也正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "s3",
        "ddb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看一眼边界内的命名：'Amazon Alexa'作为平台名称，和边界名称重复了，会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alexa",
        "alexa_boundary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "确实有点。但边界是'Amazon Alexa'，内部系统也是'Amazon Alexa'——一个是生态边界，一个是具体平台实例。在C4里这种嵌套是允许的，读者能从上下文区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alexa_boundary",
        "alexa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了。那技能的西班牙语名称'Bilbioteca Personal Skill'需要调整拼写吗？看起来像是'Biblioteca'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "skill"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，是'Biblioteca'，我拼错了。应该是'Biblioteca Personal Skill'，B-i-b-l-i-o-t-e-c-a。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "skill"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正为'Biblioteca Personal Skill'。现在所有元素都检查完毕：Usuario、Amazon Alexa边界、内部Alexa平台、技能、S3、DynamoDB，以及六条关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "skill",
        "user",
        "alexa_boundary",
